### Test Workflow Orchestrator API

### 1. Initiate a new workflow item
POST http://localhost:8080/orchestrator/workflow-items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "headline": "Database Migration",
  "narrative": "Migrate legacy database to new schema"
}

### 2. Enumerate all workflow items
GET http://localhost:8080/orchestrator/workflow-items?pageIndex=0&pageCapacity=5

### 3. Locate specific workflow item
GET http://localhost:8080/orchestrator/workflow-items/1

### 4. Transition workflow item phase
PATCH http://localhost:8080/orchestrator/workflow-items/1/phase?phase=ACTIVE

### 5. Enumerate workflow items by phase
GET http://localhost:8080/orchestrator/workflow-items?pageIndex=0&pageCapacity=10&phase=ACTIVE

### 6. Eliminate workflow item
DELETE http://localhost:8080/orchestrator/workflow-items/1